{"tha-ap315:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap315:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap315:0.3":"Gatasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap315:1.1":"“Akaseva padam natthi, ","tha-ap315:1.2":"ambare anilanjase; ","tha-ap315:1.3":"Siddhattham jinamaddakkhim, ","tha-ap315:1.4":"gacchantam tidivangane. ","tha-ap315:2.1":"Anileneritam disva, ","tha-ap315:2.2":"sammasambuddhacivaram; ","tha-ap315:2.3":"Vitti mamahu tavade, ","tha-ap315:2.4":"disvana gamanam munim. ","tha-ap315:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap315:3.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap315:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap315:3.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap315:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap315:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap315:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap315:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma gatasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap315:6.1":"Gatasannakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}